{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block meta %}
    {% include 'common/parts/meta.html.twig' with {
        'title': 'AВЕ Системз | разработка веб-порталов и приложений для вас',
        'description': 'Создадим веб-портал или приложение для вас. Просто и гибко! Стоимость часа от 1800 руб.',
        'ogTitle': 'AВЕ Системз | разработка веб-порталов и приложений для вас',
        'ogDescription': 'Создадим веб-портал или приложение для вас. Просто и гибко! Стоимость часа от 1800 руб.',
        'ogImage': host ~ asset('build/images/main-og.webp')
    } %}
{% endblock %}

{% block stylesheets %}
    {{ parent() }}
    {{ encore_entry_link_tags('index-page') }}
{% endblock %}

{% block javascripts %}
    {{ parent() }}
    {{ encore_entry_script_tags('index-page') }}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    <section class="offer">
        <h1 class="offer__main">
            Сделаем веб-портал или приложение для вашего бизнеса!</h1>

        <h2 class="offer__desc">
            Предлагаем программные решения для улучшения коммуникации с клиентами и&nbsp;оптимизации процессов.<br/>
            Учитываем уникальные потребности вашей компании.
            <br/>Стоимость от 200000 руб. за индивидуальный проект.
        </h2>

        <div class="btn offer__cta" id="offer-cta">Запросите рассчёт</div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-us content">
        <h3 class="content__header">What we're about:</h3>

        <p class="content__block-text">
            If you have an idea of an amazing application or website,
            but just don't have the right team to do all the coding for it,
            than you've come to the right place.
            Our team of skilled specialists is here to help you.
            Together we can create the exact service you want
            and set the solid foundation for your business to grow.
        </p>
        <p class="content__simple-text">
            Starting a project comes with its fair share of challenges.
            From the initial idea to managing time effectively, there's a lot to consider.
            And let's not forget about the coding part, which is vital for the success of any high-tech endeavor.
            Finding the right person for the job is crucial.
        </p>
        <p class="content__simple-text">
            Our company specializing in mobile and web development can help you with the coding part.
            As a dedicated team of professionals, we have strong business acumen and skills
            that allow us to create fast, scalable, and reliable software.
        </p>
        <p class="content__simple-text">
            And to make the development process less risky for you, we use the iterative approach.
            So basically, after every iteration, you'll get a better service or app (in terms of business value)
            with minimal financial risks.
            Our team understands that the risk of the entire application development at once is too high for every
            business.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content our-methodologies">
        <h3 id="tools" class="content__header">Our methodologies and&nbsp;technologies</h3>
        <p class="content__simple-text">
            When it comes to backend development, we use technologies such as PHP (Symfony)
            and Java/Kotlin (a variety of libraries including Vertx and Spring).
        </p>
        <p class="content__simple-text">
            For mobile application development, we primarily rely on Flutter.
            This powerful framework allows us to create applications that are compatible
            with all major platforms simultaneously, ensuring a seamless user experience across devices.
        </p>
        <div class="content__img-container content__img-container--right">
            <img class="content__anchor-img" src="{{ asset('build/images/gears.svg') }}" alt="Our tech stack"/>
        </div>
        <p class="content__simple-text">
            Additionally, our specialists are proficient in frontend development and
            can assist you with the creation of captivating user interfaces.
            We leverage the iconic JavaScript frameworks, including Angular, ReactJs, and Vue,
            to build responsive and dynamic web applications.
        </p>
        <p class="content__simple-text">
            Our dedicated development team boasts an average experience of
            <span class="content__simple-text--stressed">five years of active coding.</span> With
            extensive expertise, we've successfully tackled numerous business tasks for many businesses,
            enabling them to achieve their goals effectively.
        </p>

        <p class="content__simple-text">
            Our teams operate using Agile methodologies, which enables us to have direct involvement
            in the process of solving business tasks. By adopting Agile practices,
            we prioritize delivering solutions that provide the highest business value.
            This approach allows us to stay responsive to evolving requirements and adapt our strategies accordingly.
            Through iterative development, frequent communication, and continuous feedback,
            we ensure that our solutions align closely with your business objectives.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content how-to-work">
        <h3 class="content__header">How to work with us</h3>

        <div class="how-to-work__process">
            <div class="how-to-work__step">
                <p class="how-to-work__dig">1</p>
                <p class="how-to-work__text">Contact us</p>
            </div>

            <div class="how-to-work__step how-to-work__step--large">
                <p class=" how-to-work__dig">2</p>
                <p class="how-to-work__text">We contact you back and discuss the project (the&nbsp;idea,
                    tasks to
                    be done, available options how job can be secured (contracts etc), the contents
                    of&nbsp;the&nbsp;first
                    iteration, etc)</p>
            </div>

            <div class="how-to-work__step">
                <p class="how-to-work__dig">3</p>
                <p class="how-to-work__text">Seal the contract and start the first iteration
                    of&nbsp;the&nbsp;project
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    {% include('common/parts/contact-form.html.twig') with {'contactFormTitle': 'Свяжитесь с нами'} %}

{% endblock %}
